			<div class="content" id="post-content-3673930">
									

<p>We are not allowing commissions at this time.</p>
<p>We have just now finally gotten a policy that most of our userbase can live with. We are in the experimental period where we see how this is going to work out. I do not think we need further wrinkles at this time.</p>
<p>When we revisit this—and we will revisit this—we can evaluate how the policy is working out. If it's working out very well, we can decide if we want to expand it to things like commissions.</p>
<p>This all said, we can't police offsite conversations.</p>

							</div>

								
